"&kcron; A Reba Bya Ibikorwa na Ibihinduka . Nka i Imizi Umukoresha , Ibigize "
"ya:  Byose Abakoresha ku i Nka Nka i Sisitemu Ibikorwa . Bya i Ububiko "
"Cyagutse na . "

